CustomField.description: Numerical Month of Renewal. I.E. 01 - January, 02 - February, etc.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Numerical value for the renewal month. I.E. for a range of 1/15 - 2/14 with a renewal date of April 2nd, the value for this field would be 4, from 4/2.
CustomField.label: Renewal Month
